Titolo: MechAssault: Phantom War

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: MechAssault: Phantom War is an action video game, part of the MechWarrior series and part of the BattleTech universe created by FASA. Players assume the role of a BattleMech pilot in a 3D environment with a third person view of the combat via the top screen of the DS, while the touch screen displays the inside of the cockpit and acts as the game's controls.

Genere: Action 

Valutazione: N/A
